---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getClientSafeDomesticSymbolRecords } from '../lib/symbol-master/domesticSymbolMaster';

const clientSafeDomesticSymbols = getClientSafeDomesticSymbolRecords();
const clientSafeDomesticSymbolPayload = JSON.stringify(clientSafeDomesticSymbols)
  .replaceAll('<', '\\u003c');
---

<Layout title="Chart AI | MK Stock Lab" activePath="/chart-ai">
  <header class="page-header">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Chart AI</p>
      <h1>차트 분석 준비 화면</h1>
      <p class="lead">국내 종목을 검색해 샘플 분석 화면을 확인할 수 있습니다. 현재 화면은 <strong>샘플 종목 데이터와 예시 분석 데이터</strong>를 사용하며, AI · 시세 · 차트 연결은 이후 단계에서 진행합니다.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="chart-ai-shell">
    <section class="panel chart-ai-control-panel" aria-labelledby="chart-ai-control-heading">
      <div class="chart-ai-search-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">국내 주식·ETF</p>
          <h2 id="chart-ai-control-heading">국내 종목 검색</h2>
        </div>
        <span class="chart-ai-sample-data-badge">샘플 종목 데이터</span>
      </div>

      <div class="chart-ai-search-workbench">
        <div class="chart-ai-search-column">
          <div class="chart-ai-symbol-row">
            <label class="chart-search-shell" for="chartAiInput">
              <span>종목 코드 또는 이름</span>
              <input
                id="chartAiInput"
                type="search"
                placeholder="005930, 삼성, KODEX …"
                aria-label="국내 종목 코드 또는 이름 검색"
                aria-controls="chartAiSearchResults"
                aria-describedby="chartAiSearchExamples"
                aria-autocomplete="list"
                aria-expanded="true"
                role="combobox"
                autocomplete="off"
                spellcheck="false"
              />
            </label>
            <button class="button-link chart-ai-run-btn" id="chartAiRunBtn" type="button">
              선택 종목 분석 보기
            </button>
          </div>

          <p class="chart-ai-search-examples" id="chartAiSearchExamples">
            검색 예시: 005930 · 삼성 · 000660 · 하이닉스 · 069500 · KODEX
          </p>

          <div class="chart-ai-filter-bar" role="group" aria-label="종목 유형 필터">
            <button class="chart-ai-filter-btn active" type="button" data-asset-filter="all" aria-pressed="true">전체</button>
            <button class="chart-ai-filter-btn" type="button" data-asset-filter="stock" aria-pressed="false">주식</button>
            <button class="chart-ai-filter-btn" type="button" data-asset-filter="etf" aria-pressed="false">ETF</button>
          </div>

          <div class="chart-ai-results-head">
            <strong>검색 결과</strong>
            <span id="chartAiResultCount" aria-live="polite">0개</span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="chart-ai-search-results"
            id="chartAiSearchResults"
            role="listbox"
            aria-label="국내 종목 검색 결과"
          ></div>
          <p class="chart-ai-empty-state" id="chartAiEmptyState" hidden>
            조건에 맞는 샘플 종목이 없습니다. 종목 코드나 이름을 다시 확인해 주세요.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="chart-ai-selection-card" aria-labelledby="chart-ai-selection-heading" aria-live="polite">
          <p class="eyebrow" id="chart-ai-selection-heading">선택 종목</p>
          <div class="chart-ai-selection-title">
            <strong id="chartAiSelectedName">삼성전자</strong>
            <span id="chartAiSelectedSymbol">005930</span>
          </div>
          <dl class="chart-ai-selection-meta">
            <div><dt>자산 유형</dt><dd id="chartAiSelectedAssetType">주식</dd></div>
            <div><dt>거래소</dt><dd id="chartAiSelectedExchange">KOSPI</dd></div>
            <div><dt>통화</dt><dd id="chartAiSelectedCurrency">KRW</dd></div>
          </dl>
          <p class="chart-ai-selection-copy">선택한 샘플 종목 기준의 데모 분석 화면입니다.</p>
        </aside>
      </div>

      <p class="chart-ai-local-note">
        <span class="chart-ai-local-badge">실제 시세 아님</span>
        검색과 선택은 브라우저에 포함된 안전한 샘플 종목 데이터만 사용합니다.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel chart-ai-snapshot" aria-label="차트 스냅샷 영역">
      <div class="chart-ai-snapshot-header">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">차트 스냅샷</p>
          <h2 id="chartAiSnapshotTitle">005930 · 삼성전자 · 일봉 예시</h2>
        </div>
        <span class="chart-ai-snapshot-badge">샘플 차트</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-skeleton" aria-hidden="true" id="chartAiSnapshotBars">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </div>
      <p class="chart-ai-snapshot-note">차트 스냅샷은 이후 단계에서 연결됩니다. 현재는 시각적 예시 영역입니다.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="chart-ai-result-section" id="chartAiResultSection" aria-labelledby="chart-ai-result-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">예시 분석 결과</p>
      <h2 id="chart-ai-result-heading">
        <span id="chartAiResultSymbol">005930</span>&nbsp;·&nbsp;<span id="chartAiResultName">삼성전자</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="chart-ai-result-note" id="chartAiResultProfile">국내 대형 기술주 예시 · 일봉 예시</p>

      <div class="chart-ai-result-grid">
        <div class="panel chart-ai-result-card">
          <p class="chart-ai-card-label">추세 요약</p>
          <p class="chart-ai-card-value" id="chartAiTrend">상승 전환을 시도하는 구간으로 가정한 예시 분석입니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="panel chart-ai-result-card">
          <p class="chart-ai-card-label">모멘텀</p>
          <p class="chart-ai-card-value" id="chartAiMomentum">단기 모멘텀은 중립에서 개선되는 흐름으로 표시합니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="panel chart-ai-result-card">
          <p class="chart-ai-card-label">변동성</p>
          <p class="chart-ai-card-value" id="chartAiVolatility">변동성은 보통 수준으로 가정합니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="panel chart-ai-result-card">
          <p class="chart-ai-card-label">지지 / 저항</p>
          <ul class="status-list chart-ai-support-list">
            <li><span>지지</span><strong id="chartAiSupport">예시 지지 구간</strong></li>
            <li><span>저항</span><strong id="chartAiResistance">예시 저항 구간</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="panel chart-ai-result-card chart-ai-result-card--risk">
          <p class="chart-ai-card-label">리스크 체크</p>
          <p class="chart-ai-card-value" id="chartAiRisk">거래량 확인 전까지 추세 신뢰도는 제한적입니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel chart-ai-template-state" id="chartAiTemplateState" hidden aria-live="polite">
      <p class="eyebrow" id="chartAiTemplateEyebrow">분석 템플릿 준비 중</p>
      <p id="chartAiTemplateMsg">선택한 샘플 종목 기준의 데모 분석 화면입니다. 예시 분석 데이터는 준비 중입니다.</p>
    </section>

    <aside class="panel chart-ai-disclaimer" aria-label="이용 안내">
      <p class="eyebrow">이용 안내</p>
      <ul class="chart-ai-disclaimer-list">
        <li>이 화면의 종목과 분석 내용은 <strong>샘플 데이터</strong>입니다. AI 분석 결과가 아닙니다.</li>
        <li>시세, 차트 데이터, AI 모델은 아직 연결되지 않았습니다.</li>
        <li>투자 판단 참고용 화면이 아니며, 매매 판단에 사용할 수 없습니다.</li>
        <li>제공되는 정보는 특정 종목의 매수 또는 매도를 권고하지 않습니다.</li>
        <li>최종 투자 결정 및 그에 따른 결과는 전적으로 이용자 본인의 책임입니다.</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <script
    id="chartAiDomesticSymbolData"
    type="application/json"
    set:html={clientSafeDomesticSymbolPayload}
  ></script>

  <script>
    import { searchClientSafeDomesticSymbols } from '../lib/symbol-master/clientSymbolSearch';
    import type {
      ClientSafeSymbolSearchRecord,
      DomesticAssetType,
    } from '../lib/symbol-master/types';

    type DemoEntry = {
      symbol: string;
      name: string;
      profile: string;
      timeframe: string;
      trend: string;
      momentum: string;
      volatility: string;
      support: string;
      resistance: string;
      risk: string;
    };

    const DEMO_ANALYSIS: Record<string, DemoEntry> = {
      '005930': {
        symbol: '005930', name: '삼성전자', profile: '국내 대형 기술주 예시', timeframe: '일봉 예시',
        trend: '상승 전환을 시도하는 구간으로 가정한 예시 분석입니다.',
        momentum: '단기 모멘텀은 중립에서 개선되는 흐름으로 표시합니다.',
        volatility: '변동성은 보통 수준으로 가정합니다.',
        support: '예시 지지 구간', resistance: '예시 저항 구간',
        risk: '거래량 확인 전까지 추세 신뢰도는 제한적입니다.',
      },
      '035420': {
        symbol: '035420', name: 'NAVER', profile: '국내 인터넷 대형주 예시', timeframe: '일봉 예시',
        trend: '횡보 후 반등을 모색하는 구간으로 가정한 예시 분석입니다.',
        momentum: '단기 모멘텀은 하락에서 중립으로 전환 중인 흐름으로 표시합니다.',
        volatility: '변동성은 평균 수준으로 가정합니다.',
        support: '예시 지지 구간', resistance: '예시 저항 구간',
        risk: '이동평균선 수렴 여부를 추가 확인하는 예시 항목입니다.',
      },
    };

    const assetTypeLabel = (assetType: DomesticAssetType): string => {
      if (assetType === 'stock') return '주식';
      if (assetType === 'etf') return 'ETF';
      if (assetType === 'etn') return 'ETN';
      return '기타';
    };

    const parseClientSafeRecords = (): ClientSafeSymbolSearchRecord[] => {
      const payload = document.getElementById('chartAiDomesticSymbolData')?.textContent ?? '[]';
      try {
        const parsed: unknown = JSON.parse(payload);
        return Array.isArray(parsed) ? parsed as ClientSafeSymbolSearchRecord[] : [];
      } catch {
        return [];
      }
    };

    const setup = () => {
      const input = document.getElementById('chartAiInput') as HTMLInputElement | null;
      const runBtn = document.getElementById('chartAiRunBtn') as HTMLButtonElement | null;
      const resultsEl = document.getElementById('chartAiSearchResults');
      const resultCount = document.getElementById('chartAiResultCount');
      const emptyState = document.getElementById('chartAiEmptyState');
      const snapshotTitle = document.getElementById('chartAiSnapshotTitle');
      const resultSection = document.getElementById('chartAiResultSection');
      const templateState = document.getElementById('chartAiTemplateState');
      const templateMsg = document.getElementById('chartAiTemplateMsg');
      const filterButtons = document.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('.chart-ai-filter-btn');
      const records = parseClientSafeRecords();
      let activeFilter: DomesticAssetType | 'all' = 'all';
      let selectedSymbol = '005930';
      let visibleRecords: ClientSafeSymbolSearchRecord[] = [];

      if (!input || !runBtn || !resultsEl || !resultCount || !emptyState) return;
      if (runBtn.dataset.ready === 'true') return;
      runBtn.dataset.ready = 'true';

      const setText = (id: string, text: string) => {
        const element = document.getElementById(id);
        if (element) element.textContent = text;
      };

      const renderAnalysis = (record: ClientSafeSymbolSearchRecord) => {
        const data = DEMO_ANALYSIS[record.symbol];
        if (snapshotTitle) {
          snapshotTitle.textContent = data
            ? `${record.symbol} · ${record.nameKo} · ${data.timeframe}`
            : `${record.symbol} · ${record.nameKo} · 샘플 차트`;
        }

        if (data) {
          if (resultSection) resultSection.hidden = false;
          if (templateState) templateState.hidden = true;
          setText('chartAiResultSymbol', data.symbol);
          setText('chartAiResultName', data.name);
          setText('chartAiResultProfile', `${data.profile} · ${data.timeframe}`);
          setText('chartAiTrend', data.trend);
          setText('chartAiMomentum', data.momentum);
          setText('chartAiVolatility', data.volatility);
          setText('chartAiSupport', data.support);
          setText('chartAiResistance', data.resistance);
          setText('chartAiRisk', data.risk);
          return;
        }

        if (resultSection) resultSection.hidden = true;
        if (templateState) templateState.hidden = false;
        if (templateMsg) {
          templateMsg.textContent = `${record.symbol} (${record.nameKo}) 선택 완료. 선택한 샘플 종목 기준의 데모 분석 화면이며, 예시 분석 데이터는 준비 중입니다.`;
        }
      };

      const updateSelection = (record: ClientSafeSymbolSearchRecord) => {
        selectedSymbol = record.symbol;
        input.value = record.symbol;
        setText('chartAiSelectedName', record.nameKo);
        setText('chartAiSelectedSymbol', record.symbol);
        setText('chartAiSelectedAssetType', assetTypeLabel(record.assetType));
        setText('chartAiSelectedExchange', record.exchange);
        setText('chartAiSelectedCurrency', record.currency);
        renderAnalysis(record);
        renderResults();
      };

      const renderResults = () => {
        visibleRecords = searchClientSafeDomesticSymbols(records, {
          query: input.value,
          limit: 15,
          assetTypes: activeFilter === 'all' ? undefined : [activeFilter],
          includeStatuses: ['active'],
        });
        resultsEl.replaceChildren();
        resultCount.textContent = `${visibleRecords.length}개`;
        emptyState.hidden = visibleRecords.length > 0;
        input.setAttribute('aria-expanded', String(visibleRecords.length > 0));

        for (const record of visibleRecords) {
          const button = document.createElement('button');
          const isSelected = record.symbol === selectedSymbol;
          button.type = 'button';
          button.className = 'chart-ai-search-result';
          button.dataset.symbol = record.symbol;
          button.setAttribute('role', 'option');
          button.setAttribute('aria-selected', String(isSelected));
          button.classList.toggle('selected', isSelected);

          const identity = document.createElement('span');
          identity.className = 'chart-ai-result-identity';
          const name = document.createElement('strong');
          name.textContent = record.nameKo;
          const symbol = document.createElement('span');
          symbol.textContent = record.symbol;
          identity.append(name, symbol);

          const metadata = document.createElement('span');
          metadata.className = 'chart-ai-result-metadata';
          metadata.textContent = `${assetTypeLabel(record.assetType)} · ${record.exchange} · ${record.currency}`;
          button.append(identity, metadata);
          button.addEventListener('click', () => updateSelection(record));
          resultsEl.append(button);
        }
      };

      filterButtons.forEach((button) => {
        button.addEventListener('click', () => {
          const filter = button.dataset.assetFilter;
          if (filter !== 'all' && filter !== 'stock' && filter !== 'etf') return;
          activeFilter = filter;
          filterButtons.forEach((candidate) => {
            const active = candidate === button;
            candidate.classList.toggle('active', active);
            candidate.setAttribute('aria-pressed', String(active));
          });
          renderResults();
        });
      });

      input.addEventListener('input', renderResults);
      input.addEventListener('keydown', (event: KeyboardEvent) => {
        if (event.key === 'Enter') {
          event.preventDefault();
          runBtn.click();
        }
        if (event.key === 'ArrowDown') {
          const firstResult = resultsEl.querySelector<HTMLButtonElement>('.chart-ai-search-result');
          if (firstResult) {
            event.preventDefault();
            firstResult.focus();
          }
        }
      });
      runBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        if (visibleRecords[0]) updateSelection(visibleRecords[0]);
      });

      renderResults();
    };

    document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', setup);
    setup();
  </script>

  <style>
    .chart-ai-search-heading,
    .chart-ai-results-head,
    .chart-ai-selection-title,
    .chart-ai-result-identity {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .chart-ai-search-heading h2 {
      margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
    }

    .chart-ai-sample-data-badge,
    .chart-ai-filter-btn {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--surface-muted);
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font: inherit;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .chart-ai-sample-data-badge {
      padding: 0.4rem 0.7rem;
    }

    .chart-ai-search-workbench {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.65fr) minmax(220px, 0.85fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
    }

    .chart-ai-search-column,
    .chart-ai-selection-card {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .chart-ai-search-examples {
      margin: 0.55rem 0 0;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      overflow-wrap: anywhere;
    }

    .chart-ai-filter-bar {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.45rem;
      margin: 0.9rem 0;
    }

    .chart-ai-filter-btn {
      min-height: 34px;
      padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .chart-ai-filter-btn.active,
    .chart-ai-filter-btn[aria-pressed='true'] {
      border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 55%, var(--border));
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 12%, var(--surface));
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .chart-ai-results-head {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }

    .chart-ai-search-results {
      max-height: 286px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      overscroll-behavior: contain;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--surface);
      scrollbar-gutter: stable;
    }

    .chart-ai-search-result {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 58px;
      padding: 0.7rem 0.8rem;
      border: 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text);
      font: inherit;
      text-align: left;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .chart-ai-search-result:last-child {
      border-bottom: 0;
    }

    .chart-ai-search-result:hover,
    .chart-ai-search-result.selected {
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 8%, var(--surface));
    }

    .chart-ai-search-result.selected {
      box-shadow: inset 3px 0 0 var(--primary);
    }

    .chart-ai-search-result:focus-visible,
    .chart-ai-filter-btn:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 35%, transparent);
      outline-offset: -3px;
    }

    .chart-ai-result-identity {
      justify-content: flex-start;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .chart-ai-result-identity strong {
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .chart-ai-result-identity span,
    .chart-ai-result-metadata {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .chart-ai-empty-state {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 1rem;
      border: 1px dashed var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .chart-ai-selection-card {
      align-self: start;
      padding: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 28%, var(--border));
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 9%, var(--surface)), var(--surface));
      box-shadow: inset 3px 0 0 var(--primary);
    }

    .chart-ai-selection-title {
      align-items: baseline;
      margin-top: 0.45rem;
    }

    .chart-ai-selection-title strong {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }

    .chart-ai-selection-title span {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }

    .chart-ai-selection-meta {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .chart-ai-selection-meta div {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.45rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .chart-ai-selection-meta dt,
    .chart-ai-selection-copy {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

